---
import BrandLayout from '../layouts/BrandLayout.astro';
---
<BrandLayout title="redot BRAND | 리닷 브랜드 로고">
  <div>
    <h1 class="font-[var(--font-display)] text-[32px] font-semibold">리닷 브랜드 로고</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-[16px] text-[var(--text-secondary)]">리닷의 심볼과 로고타입이 합쳐진 브랜드 로고입니다. 가이드라인을 참고해 사용하세요.</p>

    <div class="mt-6 flex items-center justify-center rounded-[16px] border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface)] p-7 shadow-[var(--shadow-soft)]">
      <img src="/assets/wordmark.svg" alt="redot 로고" />
    </div>

    <section class="mt-12">
      <h3 class="font-[var(--font-display)] text-[20px]">로고 가이드</h3>
      <div class="mt-3 flex items-center justify-center rounded-[16px] border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface-muted)] p-7 shadow-[var(--shadow-soft)]">
        <img src="/assets/logo-grid.svg" alt="로고 그리드" />
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-12">
      <h3 class="font-[var(--font-display)] text-[20px]">브랜드 로고 모션</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 text-[var(--text-secondary)]">리닷 브랜드 로고의 모션입니다. 요소들이 하나로 모이며 통합되는 순간을 강조합니다.</p>
      <div class="mt-5 flex items-center justify-center rounded-[16px] border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface)] p-7 shadow-[var(--shadow-soft)]">
        <img src="/assets/logo-motion.svg" alt="브랜드 로고 모션" />
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-12">
      <h3 class="font-[var(--font-display)] text-[20px]">리닷 심볼과 베리에이션</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 text-[var(--text-secondary)]">상황에 따라 컬러와 스타일을 선택해 사용할 수 있습니다.</p>
      <div class="mt-5 grid grid-cols-[repeat(auto-fit,minmax(160px,1fr))] gap-[18px]">
        <div class="rounded-[14px] border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface)] p-4 text-center text-[12px] text-[var(--text-tertiary)]">
          <img class="mx-auto mb-2.5 max-w-[120px]" src="/assets/symbol-default.svg" alt="default" />
          default
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-[14px] border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface)] p-4 text-center text-[12px] text-[var(--text-tertiary)]">
          <img class="mx-auto mb-2.5 max-w-[120px]" src="/assets/symbol-solid.svg" alt="solid" />
          solid
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-[14px] border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface)] p-4 text-center text-[12px] text-[var(--text-tertiary)]">
          <img class="mx-auto mb-2.5 max-w-[120px]" src="/assets/symbol-3d.svg" alt="3D" />
          3D
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-[18px] grid grid-cols-[repeat(auto-fit,minmax(160px,1fr))] gap-[18px]">
        <div class="rounded-[14px] border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface)] p-4 text-center text-[12px] text-[var(--text-tertiary)]">
          <img class="mx-auto mb-2.5 max-w-[120px]" src="/assets/wordmark.svg" alt="default" />
          default
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-[14px] border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface)] p-4 text-center text-[12px] text-[var(--text-tertiary)]">
          <img class="mx-auto mb-2.5 max-w-[120px]" src="/assets/wordmark-mono.svg" alt="mono" />
          mono
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-[18px] grid grid-cols-[repeat(auto-fit,minmax(160px,1fr))] gap-[18px]">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center rounded-[16px] border border-[var(--border)] bg-[#3a79ee] p-7 text-white shadow-[var(--shadow-soft)]">
          <img src="/assets/wordmark-white.svg" alt="background blue" />
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center rounded-[16px] border border-[var(--border)] bg-[#0b0d13] p-7 text-white shadow-[var(--shadow-soft)]">
          <img src="/assets/wordmark-white.svg" alt="background black" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-12">
      <h3 class="font-[var(--font-display)] text-[20px]">리닷 협력사 표기</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 text-[var(--text-secondary)]">리닷의 심볼과 워드마크의 조합 비율을 유지해 협력사 표기에 활용합니다.</p>
      <div class="mt-5 flex items-center justify-center rounded-[16px] border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface)] p-7 shadow-[var(--shadow-soft)]">
        <img src="/assets/partner-lockup.svg" alt="협력사 표기" />
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</BrandLayout>
